<div id="review_1337199194" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1337199194" />
    <a title="Anju Saha" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/43741872-anju-saha"><img alt="Anju Saha" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1434509533p2/43741872.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1337199194?book_show_action=true">Jul 16, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Anju Saha" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Anju Saha" href="/user/show/43741872-anju-saha">Anju Saha</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/43741872-anju-saha?shelf=indie">indie</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1337199194" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13673568621223941239">Makes you feel it is written about your own life experiences.<br/>Pankaj Varma has done a brilliant job in re-creating the Partition days. And his description of the behaviour of the dementia state replicated, almost entirely, what I had seen with my own mother. The empathy one feels while reading the book was totally unexpected. Superbly done.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

<tr class="no_border feedFooterReview" id="update_comment_stuff_Review1337199194">
